    • addToSelectedDonuts

      private void addToSelectedDonuts(String selection)
      This method adds a donut item key value pair into the hashmap representing the list of donuts waiting to be submitted to the order. The key is the flavor and the value is the quantity and donut type.
      Parameters:
      selection - String which contains information of the donut item.

    • removeFromSelectedDonuts

      private void removeFromSelectedDonuts(String flavor)
      This method removes a donut item key value pair from the hashmap representing the list of donuts waiting to be submitted to the order. The key is the flavor, which is used to retrieve the pair.
      Parameters:
      flavor - String which contains the donut flavor.

    • addDonutTypeComboBoxListener

      private void addDonutTypeComboBoxListener()
      This method takes care of adding a listener to the donut type combobox for any new value changes. The listener updates the image view and available flavors list view depending on the selected donut type.
